          <li style="margin-right:7px;color:white;"><a href="/user/logout" style="color:white;">Logout</a></li>
        </div>

      <% } else { %>
        <li style="margin-right:12px;color:white;"><a href="/login/login" style="color:white;">Login</a></li>
      <% } %>
      </ul>

      </div>

  <br/>
  <hr/>

  <!-- 상단바 끝 -->


<br/>

  <div class="delete-top-box">
  </div>

  <hr style="background-color: #2F5971;
  height: 2px;
  margin-top: 20px;
  width: 100%;
  float: left;">



  <div class ="box1" style=" align-items:center;">
    <br>
    <p id="font" style="margin-top:60px;"> 회원 탈퇴를 하시면 개인정보, 저장된 리뷰데이터 등이 모두 삭제됩니다.<br> 그래도 탈퇴하시겠습니까? </p>
    <br>
    <div style="margin-top:50px;">
      <span style="float:left; margin-top:5px; margin-left:50px;color:#2F5971; font-size:16px;" id="font" > 비밀번호 확인 </span>
      <input type="password" id="password" style="margin-left:22px;" class="email-input" name="password" />
    </div>
